    <content><![CDATA[<p><code>Hexo Next</code> 在使用中遇到的问题与结局办法汇总。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<pre class="highlight"><code class="bash">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span>  
$ hexo new -p  notation/pm2/pm2-简单教程
$ hexo clean  
$ hexo generate
$ hexo server  
$ hexo deploy
</code></pre>
